item.title: Small Bit of help
item.dc:creator: @TeleNubby TeleNubby
item.description:
@TeleNubby wrote:

Change

NPCHandler.newNPC(2627, absX-1, absY, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 10);

To

NPCHandler.newNPC(2627, absX-1, absY, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 10, true);

Next time read the error message. The parameters you supplied did not meet those of the method existing.
